# Cursor Rules for Stockholm Plastikkirurgi

## Design System & Styling Guidelines

### Color Usage

- **Primary text color**: Always use `text-brand-black` for main text content
- **Brand colors**: Use brand-specific color classes when available
- **Consistency**: Maintain consistent color usage across all components

### File Structure

- Components go in `/components/` directory
- UI components go in `/components/ui/`
- Sections go in `/components/sections/`
- Services go in `/services/` directory
- Types go in `/types/` directory

### Components

- **Image component**: Always use the nextjs image component when using images.
